          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不肖而无德，不堪为君，意欲传位于贤，以让有德之人，岂不是一国之利，万"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "民之福。孤在宫中，不知外事，千里一俊，百里一贤，众卿必有所知。奏与孤"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "家，以便恭请。万不可徒震其名，不察其实，使孤传位于非人，遗害于天下也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁以君位公于天下，传贤不传子，足征圣德高深，真万民之福也。臣等夙知"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "布衣许由，乃当今贤者，品行清高，学识深远，敬举此人以继帝位，天下幸甚，"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "未知圣意如何？"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一人之智识有限，万民之舆论无私。既卿等同举此人，必名下无虚，但不知现"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "居何地？"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就在都城外三十里浮云村内居住。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好！吩咐御林军保驾，众卿随孤一同前去迎接便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等领旨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "御林军走上！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四大铠、四武士、金瓜钺斧同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四朝臣",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "起驾浮云村。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤登基恶民所恶好民所好，"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "国承平民安泰快乐逍遥。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为国民谋治安传位贤豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "全不想与百姓原是同胞。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怎忍得天下人鬼哭神嚎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "反不如官天下免动枪刀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "因此上访许由亲到荒郊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "尧帝",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "免得孤担重任国事勤劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "朝臣甲→四朝臣",
