    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "巢父"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（巢父牵牛上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "心比寒梅傲骨清，"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤芳自赏乐天真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "拂去三斗软红尘。"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老汉，巢父。自幼秉性清高，为人固执，生在于今世界，语言动静，俱不合时"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宜。因此隐居在这浮云村，与世人不通往来，自种自食，日出而作，日入而息，"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "任天行乐，却也逍遥自在。村中有一人许由，也是个清洁君子，我与他为友，"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "颇甚相见。看溪边水清，不免牵牛去饮便了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "巢父",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "牵牛去向溪边饮，"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
          "stage_direction": 4,
          "唱": 1
        },
        "singing_ratio": 1.0,
        "dominant_style_family": "西皮",
        "musical_styles": [
